title: BONUS EPISODE: George Birge Interview
itunes:title: BONUS EPISODE: George Birge Interview
description:
Bobby had George Birge in studio to discuss his journey on becoming a country singer. They talked about George’s first passion, golf, and working toward that goal. Then moving on to his love for music, starting a band in high school, down to the moment he decided to begin writing, and going solo as an artist. George also shares the moment he met country music icons Clay Walker and Gary Allan.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
